page.title: 09A Holiday weekend by Lee
page.content: On Saturday we went to York for the weekend to stay with my cousins Jacquie and Mellisa.On Sunday morning we got up and dressed and had breakfast together.Then we went out to play.It was a sunny day and we played hide and seek.At twelve o'clock we had dinner and at one o'clock we changed for the prayer meeting.We got home at 5-30.We had tea.We had beefburgers,ice cream,cakes and sweets.After tea we played out at a hotel having pop and crisps.In the garden there were swings and there was a boat on the river.When we got home we had supper and went to bed.
